Cell["\<\
Then, we  define  SO (N - 1), which  is  the  remaining  symmetry  after  SO \
(N)  has  been  broken .\
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9333002281916857`*^9, 3.933300265193598*^9}, {
  3.933300322062821*^9, 
